      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHARLI'S BEGONIA (8) was rewarded for her honesty after two minors on end with a deserved win last time, scoring at this track over 352m (19.56). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Expected to be right there at the finish again. EXPELLED (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (19.99) in a Free For All at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. OUT OF AUSTRIAN (1) missed the frame latest when fifth at this track (19.91) but scored five back at this track (19.96). Solid record here at the distance winning six races. A big run wouldn't surprise. GOLDSTAR RODNEY (2) can measure up with the right run.",
